  <entry>
    <title>Emmet使用手册</title>
    <link href="http://blog.weson.cf/2016/09/03/Emmet%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C/"/>
    <id>http://blog.weson.cf/2016/09/03/Emmet使用手册/</id>
    <published>2016-09-03T10:34:43.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-09-03T12:44:28.639Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="介绍"><a href="#介绍" class="headerlink" title="介绍"></a>介绍</h1><p>Emmet (前身为 Zen Coding) 是一个能大幅度提高前端开发效率的一个工具，它使用仿CSS选择器的语法来生成代码，大大提高了HTML/CSS代码编写的速度。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h1 id="语法"><a href="#语法" class="headerlink" title="语法"></a>语法</h1><h2 id="HTML缩写"><a href="#HTML缩写" class="headerlink" title="HTML缩写"></a>HTML缩写</h2><h3 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h3><p>HTML文档需要包含一些固定的标签，比如<html>、<head>、</head><body>等，现在你只需要1秒钟就可以输入这些标签。比如输入“!”或“html:5”，然后按拓展键（默认为Tab键，不行的可以试试Ctrl+E）：</body></html></p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"en"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>Document<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    </div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>html:5 或!：用于HTML5文档类型</li>
<li>html:xt：用于XHTML过渡文档类型</li>
<li>html:4s：用于HTML4严格文档类型<h3 id="id和类属性"><a href="#id和类属性" class="headerlink" title="id和类属性"></a>id和类属性</h3>缩写：#header<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;<span class="selector-tag">div</span> id=<span class="string">"header"</span>&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>缩写：.title<br><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;<span class="selector-tag">div</span> class=<span class="string">"title"</span>&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>缩写：form#search.wide<br><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;<span class="selector-tag">form</span> id=<span class="string">"search"</span> class=<span class="string">"wide"</span>&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>缩写：p.class1.class2.class3<br><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;<span class="selector-tag">p</span> class=<span class="string">"class1 class2 class3"</span>&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="文本"><a href="#文本" class="headerlink" title="文本"></a>文本</h3><p>缩写：a{Click me}</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;<span class="selector-tag">a</span> href=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;Click me&lt;/a&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="嵌套"><a href="#嵌套" class="headerlink" title="嵌套"></a>嵌套</h3><p>>：子元素符号，表示嵌套的元素<br>缩写：nav&gt;ul&gt;li<br><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;nav&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;ul&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/ul&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/nav&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>+：同级标签符号<br>缩写：div+p</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>^：可以使该符号后的标签提升一级<br>缩写：div&gt;p^span</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="分组"><a href="#分组" class="headerlink" title="分组"></a>分组</h3><p>缩写：div&gt;(header&gt;ul&gt;li&gt;a)+footer</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;header&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;ul&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;li&gt;&lt;<span class="selector-tag">a</span> href=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;/ul&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/header&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;footer&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/footer&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="乘法（定义多个元素）"><a href="#乘法（定义多个元素）" class="headerlink" title="乘法（定义多个元素）"></a>乘法（定义多个元素）</h3><p>缩写：ul&gt;li*5<br><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;ul&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/ul&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="自增"><a href="#自增" class="headerlink" title="自增"></a>自增</h3><p>缩写：ul&gt;li.item$*5</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;ul&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;<span class="selector-tag">li</span> class=<span class="string">"item1"</span>&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;<span class="selector-tag">li</span> class=<span class="string">"item2"</span>&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;<span class="selector-tag">li</span> class=<span class="string">"item3"</span>&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;<span class="selector-tag">li</span> class=<span class="string">"item4"</span>&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;<span class="selector-tag">li</span> class=<span class="string">"item5"</span>&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/ul&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="自定义属性"><a href="#自定义属性" class="headerlink" title="自定义属性"></a>自定义属性</h3><p>缩写：td[rowspan=2 colspan=3 title]</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;<span class="selector-tag">td</span> rowspan=<span class="string">"2"</span> colspan=<span class="string">"3"</span> title=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;&lt;/td&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="隐式标签"><a href="#隐式标签" class="headerlink" title="隐式标签"></a>隐式标签</h3><p>声明一个带类的标签，只需输入div.item，就会生成<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"item"</span>&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>在过去版本中，可以省略掉div，即输入.item即可生成<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"item"</span>&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>现在如果只输入.item，则Emmet会根据父标签进行判定。比如在<ul>中输入.item，就会生成<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;li <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"item"</span>&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></ul></p>
<p>下面是所有的隐式标签名称： </p>
<ul>
<li>li：用于ul和ol中</li>
<li>tr：用于table、tbody、thead和tfoot中</li>
<li>td：用于tr中</li>
<li>option：用于select和optgroup中</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="CSS缩写"><a href="#CSS缩写" class="headerlink" title="CSS缩写"></a>CSS缩写</h2><h3 id="赋值"><a href="#赋值" class="headerlink" title="赋值"></a>赋值</h3><p>缩写：w100</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">100px</span>;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>除了px，也可以生成其他单位，比如输入h10p+m5e，结果如下： </p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">10%</span>;  </div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">5em</span>;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>单位别名列表:</p>
<ul>
<li>p表示%</li>
<li>e表示em</li>
<li>x表示ex</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="附加属性"><a href="#附加属性" class="headerlink" title="附加属性"></a>附加属性</h3><p>缩写：@f+</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">@font-face &#123;  </div><div class="line">  font-family: 'FontName';  </div><div class="line">  src: url('FileName.eot');  </div><div class="line">  src: url('FileName.eot?#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),  </div><div class="line">     url('FileName.woff') format('woff'),  </div><div class="line">     url('FileName.ttf') format('truetype'),  </div><div class="line">     url('FileName.svg#FontName') format('svg');  </div><div class="line">  font-style: normal;  </div><div class="line">  font-weight: normal;  </div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="供应商前缀"><a href="#供应商前缀" class="headerlink" title="供应商前缀"></a>供应商前缀</h3><p>如果输入非W3C标准的CSS属性，Emmet会自动加上供应商前缀，比如输入trs，则会生成：</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">-webkit-<span class="attribute">transform</span>: ;  </div><div class="line">-moz-<span class="attribute">transform</span>: ;  </div><div class="line">-ms-<span class="attribute">transform</span>: ;  </div><div class="line">-o-<span class="attribute">transform</span>: ;  </div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">transform</span>: ;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>前缀缩写如下：</p>
<ul>
<li>w表示 -webkit-</li>
<li>m表示 -moz-</li>
<li>s表示 -ms-</li>
<li>o表示 -o-</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="渐变"><a href="#渐变" class="headerlink" title="渐变"></a>渐变</h3><p>缩写：lg(left, #fff 50%, #000)</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">background-image</span>: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, <span class="number">#fff</span> <span class="number">50%</span>, <span class="number">#000</span>);</div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">background-image</span>: -o-linear-gradient(left, <span class="number">#fff</span> <span class="number">50%</span>, <span class="number">#000</span>);</div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">background-image</span>: linear-gradient(to right, <span class="number">#fff</span> <span class="number">50%</span>, <span class="number">#000</span>);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    
