    <link href="http://blog.weson.cf/2016/08/27/hexo%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <id>http://blog.weson.cf/2016/08/27/hexo常用命令/</id>
    <published>2016-08-27T13:46:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-08-29T15:21:08.457Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a>常用命令</h2><blockquote>
<p>hexo new “title” #新建文章<br>hew new page “title” #新建页面<br>hexo generate #生成静态网页<br>hexo server #启动服务预览<br>hexo deploy#开始部署</p>
</blockquote>
<a id="more"></a>
<h2 id="命令简写"><a href="#命令简写" class="headerlink" title="命令简写"></a>命令简写</h2><blockquote>
<p>hexo n “我的博客” == hexo new “我的博客” #新建文章<br>hexo p == hexo publish<br>hexo g== hexo generate #生成静态网页<br>hexo s == hexo server #启动服务预览<br>hexo d == hexo deploy#开始部署</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="命令合并"><a href="#命令合并" class="headerlink" title="命令合并"></a>命令合并</h2><blockquote>
<p>hexo d -g #生成静态网页并部署</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
    
